        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: Permanent</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 10&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>This spell makes spoiled, rotten, poisonous, or otherwise contaminated food and water pure and suitable for eating and drinking. One of the following may be affected:</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Drink: </strong>6 quarts.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Rations: </strong>One trail ration (iron or standard).</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Unpreserved food: </strong>A quantity sufficient for 12 human-sized beings.</p>",
