        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 2 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: The caster or a creature touched</strong></p>\n<p>The creature touched is calmed and purged of fear. Magically induced fear may be dispelled, but this requires the subject to make a Mental save. The save is modified by -1 per level of the caster.</p>\n<p><strong>Reversed: Cause Fear</strong></p>\n<p>Will cause a target within 120&rsquo; to flee for the duration unless it saves versus spells.</p>",
