        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 6 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 30&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>All creatures within range are protected from cold, as follows:</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Normal cold: </strong>Unharmed by non-magical freezing temperatures.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Save bonus: </strong>Gain a +2 bonus to all saving throws versus cold-based magical or breath attacks.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Cold-based damage:</strong> Is reduced by 1 point per damage die rolled. (Each die inflicts a minimum of 1 hit point damage.)</p>",
